IDR Banknotes Dataset

A processed dataset of Indonesian Rupiah (IDR) banknote images for
Machine Learning and Computer Vision.

Attribution

This dataset is derived from the Rupiah Banknotes Dataset by M. Kaspul Anwar.

Original repository:
https://github.com/mkaspulanwar/rupiah-banknotes-dataset

Modifications:
- Removed image metadata
- Compressed images
- Reorganized dataset structure

